main event: While on patrol, observers noted a white object appearing bright as lightning, visible for about 7 minutes, and moving from due South to due Southwest.
interesting points: The object exhibited a vapor trail and wind effect,The sighting was logged under Project 10073,The object was described as comparable in size and speed to jestors,The observation took place on 27 Oct 61,The report included communication details from various military divisions.
sighted object: one white object in the sky
